{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GyvbzVQphMktHZXHzGkq8M","type":"tool_result","content":"=========== skew-job-broadcast.yaml ===========\napiVersion: batch/v1\nkind: Job\nmetadata:\n  name: spark-skew-broadcast\n  namespace: spark-skew\nspec:\n  backoffLimit: 0\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        app: spark-skew\n        strategy: broadcast\n    spec:\n      serviceAccountName: spark\n      restartPolicy: Never\n      containers:\n      - name: spark-skew\n        image: apache/spark:3.5.3\n        env:\n        - name: STRATEGY\n          value: \"broadcast\"\n        command:\n        - /bin/bash\n        - -c\n        - |\n          set -e\n          export SPARK_LOCAL_IP=$(hostname -i)\n          echo \"STRATEGY=broadcast (broadcast small products table, avoids skewed shuffle)\"\n          echo \"\" | base64 -d > /tmp/skew_broadcast.py\n          /opt/spark/bin/spark-submit \\\n            --master local[2] \\\n            --conf spark.sql.autoBroadcastJoinThreshold=10485760 \\\n            /tmp/skew_broadcast.py\n          echo \"spark_skew_broadcast_complete\"\n        resources:\n          requests:\n            cpu: 200m\n            memory: 256Mi\n          limits:\n            cpu: 500m\n            memory: 512Mi\n=========== skew-job-aqe.yaml ===========\napiVersion: batch/v1\nkind: Job\nmetadata:\n  name: spark-skew-aqe\n  namespace: spark-skew\nspec:\n  backoffLimit: 0\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        app: spark-skew\n        strategy: aqe\n    spec:\n      serviceAccountName: spark\n      restartPolicy: Never\n      containers:\n      - name: spark-skew\n        image: apache/spark:3.5.3\n        env:\n        - name: STRATEGY\n          value: \"aqe\"\n        command:\n        - /bin/bash\n        - -c\n        - |\n          set -e\n          export SPARK_LOCAL_IP=$(hostname -i)\n          echo \"STRATEGY=aqe (Adaptive Query Execution auto-splits skewed partitions)\"\n     